name: DongHyuk Kim's Website
body:
## Welcome to **DongHyuk Kim's** website.
* This website is made for the CSE199 project.
* My major is Computer Science.
* We learn something through [`internet-class.org`](https://www.internet-class.org)

Our instructor is Geoffrey Challen  
He is **great instructor for computer science.**  
He is **passionate instructor.**

## In this course, we learn about  
* [The Internet Era](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Information_Age)
* [Connectivity](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Connectivity)
* [Protocols](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Protocol)
* [Routing](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Routing)
* [Transport](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Transport_layer)
* [Naming](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hostname)
* [Web](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Web)
* [Search](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Online_search)
* [Security](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Network_security)
* [Identity](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Identity)
* [The Interactive Web](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Interactive_media)
* [The Mobile and Pervasive Web](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Web_application)
* [Your Brain on the Internet](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Psychological_effects_of_Internet_use)
* [Internet Content and Economics](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Digital_economy)
* [Lost and Future Visions of the Internet](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Future_Internet)
